This spell, born of the lesser hallucinating type magics, delves deeper<br>
and affects another level of the mind.  A victim of this spell will find<br>
himself out of control, literally frothing at the mouth.  Those nearby<br>
should get away quickly, as what the person may do is completely<br>
unpredictable.  <br>
